data.description: Video Walkthru: https://tyler-fraser-real-estate-photography.aryeo.com/videos/0ffb1c7c-656c-439c-9d34-4191cfd447cd.  This stately home perched atop a private mountain knob with expansive long range views of The Great Smoky Mountains National Park with all brand new POOL! Conveniently located 5 minutes to the 407 exit ''Gateway To The Smokies''! With 4 generously appointed bedrooms and 5.5 bathrooms, this 5.15 acre property is the epitome of refined living. Step inside and be greeted by the expansive living spaces, adorned with exquisite detailing, soaring ceilings, and abundant natural light. The chef's kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring top-of-the-line Subzero and Dacor appliances. Master suite with easy pool access, a spa-like ensuite bathroom, and ample his and hers closet space. Three additional bedrooms offer privacy and comfort for family and guests. Step outside to discover your own private oasis with an all brand NEW POOL. This stately home also boasts a home office, and lower level ''apartment/in-law style'' on the lowest level with plenty of living space. Additional amenities include a butler's pantry, a 3-car garage, pool access from jack-and-jill bath, brand new whole house water system, new hot water heater, and new wine fridge. This property has the ability to be short term rental, vacation home, or even a wonderful primary residence. Bucee's just went in at the 407 exit and much more is set to be developed!
